# Krasny Yar, Zaigrayevsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Krasny Yar () is a rural locality (a selo) in Zaigrayevsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 30 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Krasny Yar is located 59&nbsp;km northeast of Zaigrayevo (the district's administrative centre) by road. Angir is the nearest rural locality.
